  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','2cbeed4e-91d5-4048-ad81-eb122986b648','approved','human_observation','A3 Behold the Banner: places 50% Ally Protection on all allies except Acelin for 2 turns. Guaranteed (no chance roll). CD 5 unbooked / 3 fully booked. AyumiLove (human read).','ayumilove-human-read-july-2026',now(),0,null,'unknown',null,null,'bulk-approve-2026-07-11',now()),
  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','8dd046f2-679c-4ff5-9b38-987b7a6af674','approved','human_observation','A2 Shield Crush: AoE attack dealing damage equal to the total Shield value removed, capped at 1000% DEF. Not a debuff, not ACC-gated. AyumiLove (human read).','ayumilove-human-read-july-2026',now(),0,null,'unknown',null,null,'bulk-approve-2026-07-11',now()),
  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','69e1a96c-45b6-4f5d-ac8f-ca91d0314265','approved','human_observation','Aura: Increases Ally DEF in All Battles by 25% (all allies, faction-agnostic). NOTE: Acelin also has a Faction Unity HP +15% aura that applies ONLY to Banner Lords allies — intentionally NOT tagged separately until the engine has faction-aware aura logic, to avoid over-crediting mixed teams. ascension_required=3 by default rule (AyumiLove cannot show gates). AyumiLove (human read).','ayumilove-human-read-july-2026',now(),3,null,'aoe',null,null,'bulk-approve-2026-07-11',now()),
  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','e2f58a30-7952-49d4-858d-a118139fe2f6','approved','human_observation','A2 Shield Crush: heals all allies by the total value of all Shield buffs on all allies, then removes those Shields. Heal scales with accumulated Shield value — optimal rotation is A3 (place Shields) then A2 (consume). CD 4 unbooked / 3 fully booked. AyumiLove (human read).','ayumilove-human-read-july-2026',now(),0,null,'unknown',null,null,'bulk-approve-2026-07-11',now()),
  ('a25dfaad-e8e8-4031-9ecf-56d334029eb7','83f82f06-cd53-4c59-8a83-1cbe8ea3a0f1','approved','human_observation','A3 Behold the Banner: also places a Shield (30% of max HP) on all allies. Feeds the A2 (Shield Crush) heal + AoE damage and the A1 RES-ignore condition. AyumiLove (human read).','ayumilove-human-read-july-2026',now(),0,null,'unknown',null,null,'bulk-approve-2026-07-11',now()),
  ('e367d6c7-30c5-4991-95f9-b57130c7b22d','0b61e5de-5494-40ff-a545-c0fdc791e386','approved','human_observation','Aura: Increases Ally ACC in All Battles by 60 — highest ACC aura in the project. As team leader adds +60 ACC to all allies, directly lifting debuff landing rates on threshold-sensitive stages. ascension_required=3 by default rule (AyumiLove cannot show gates). AyumiLove (human read).','ayumilove-human-read-july-2026',now(),3,null,'aoe',null,null,'bulk-approve-2026-07-11',now()),
  ('e367d6c7-30c5-4991-95f9-b57130c7b22d','e2f58a30-7952-49d4-858d-a118139fe2f6','approved','human_observation','A2 Healing Script: heals all allies by 25% of Adelyn''s MAX HP (also restores 25% of each ally''s destroyed MAX HP — HP-destruction recovery, minor for current dungeon scope). Guaranteed. CD 4 unbooked / 3 fully booked. AyumiLove (human read).','ayumilove-human-read-july-2026',now(),0,null,'unknown',null,null,'bulk-approve-2026-07-11',now()),
